==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pathless
<hw>Path"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no beaten
path or way; untrodden; impenetrable; <as>as, <ex>pathless</ex>
woods</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Trough the heavens' wide, <qex>pathless</qex> way.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pathmaker</ent>⟦br⟧
